data.description: Must see this 2462 Pepper Court, Townhome at Carrington Park perfection on a quiet Cul de Sac! Easy access to getting around town to shopping, schools and business. As you step inside, you are greeted by a gorgeous interior, beautiful living room, hardwood floor, kitchen with subway marble backsplash, kitchen island, nice cabinets, pantry, all stainless appliances including refrigerator and lovely dining area. The property has been well maintained.  High Ceilings and step out in backyard with wooded view. Upstairs, you’ll discover the large master bedroom and spacious walk-in closets. Total of 3 bedrooms and 2 Full-baths and half-bath downstairs. The awesome Loft area is for your extra space. Laundry room. Two car-garage and affordable monthly HOA fee. Make an appointment to show this property and send an offer!
